'''Farrberries''' were a type of large, purple berry that was considered a delicacy throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. They were prized for their fine scent and the invigorating effect they produced when eaten; the best farrberries were grown in the [[Xorth system/Legends|Xorth system]].

